{
  "stem": "7938.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was not far from the ghetto, but it was on the other side of the River of Vistula in Krakow, not far from where I-- where I lived before on the main street where the-- where the-- Of course, we had-- I had to walk, because I couldn't use the tramway, because they were not allowed.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Jews-- Jews were not allowed to-- to use it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I started working there as a mechanic, or actually in the warehouse for parts.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I knew a little bit about it, so it was easy for me to do it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The name of the firm was Steyr-Daimler.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was a big factory, the foremost German factory of cars and motorcycles.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all these cars and motorcycles came back from-- for repairs to us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had there a-- which I thought that it was a friend of mine, who was a secretary of the university in-- in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But as it appeared later, he was not such a friend.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we were going from day to day there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my wife's brother also started working there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we-- from the ghetto, we came out separately.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] As a matter of fact, I-- I-- we received permission to go to-- to the-- to the-- for to go out from the ghetto, but at the same time-- the same time, they started building concentration camp Plaszow, not far away from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they took us before, even before the liquidation of Krakow ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They told us that since we are going out into a German place, and the work was appreciated by them, they took us to the concentration camp about January.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think January, 1943.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
